WEBVTT

1
01:04:52.220 --> 01:04:55.770 
是时候让那些猴子尝尝恐惧的滋味了
Time to strike fear into the hearts of these apes.

2
01:05:03.150 --> 01:05:07.610 
在生火大师文明人面前感受绝望吧
Look upon Betterman the fire maker and despair!

3
01:05:07.690 --> 01:05:08.700 
我烧
Flame, flame!

4
01:05:12.030 --> 01:05:14.660 
好极了 现在它们有了矛 又有了火
Great. Now they have spears and fire.

5
01:05:14.740 --> 01:05:17.160 
盖 他把火送给猴子了
Guy, he just gave the monkeys fire!

